<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:32:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>明尼苏达州总检察长基思·埃里森（Keith Ellison）直言不讳地批评以色列，他告诉民主党全国委员会：哈里斯在加沙问题上正在倾听我们的意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</link><description>尽管取得了一些相对较小的胜利，亲巴勒斯坦的支持者仍然认为民主党全国代表大会有效地削弱了他们的声音</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 01:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</guid></item><item><title>“现在是时候了”：美国以色列人质的父母向民主党全国委员会发表讲话，呼吁达成协议以结束加沙的痛苦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/addressing-dnc-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-call-for-deal-to-end-to-gaza-agony/00000191-775e-dacb-afb3-ffff01e80000</link><description>乔恩·波林 (Jon Polin) 和雷切尔·戈德堡 (Rachel Goldberg) 的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 于 10 月 7 日被绑架，他们告诉民主党人，“在痛苦的竞争中，没有赢家”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 00:14:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/addressing-dnc-parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-call-for-deal-to-end-to-gaza-agony/00000191-775e-dacb-afb3-ffff01e80000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普指责舒默是哈马斯成员，并指责民主党导致以色列输掉公关战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-accuses-schumer-of-being-hamas-member-blames-democrats-for-israel-losing-pr-battle/00000191-76ed-d2f3-afdf-7ffd13cf0000</link><description>前总统还对“犹太游说团体”失去影响力表示遗憾，如果这些评论来自对 AIPAC 等组织的民主党批评者，共和党人可能会谴责这些言论为反犹太主义。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 22:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/trump-accuses-schumer-of-being-hamas-member-blames-democrats-for-israel-losing-pr-battle/00000191-76ed-d2f3-afdf-7ffd13cf0000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列组织试图撤销巴勒斯坦记者的艾美奖提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-group-tries-to-get-emmy-nomination-rescinded-from-palestinian-journalist/00000191-7667-dacb-afb3-ffff5ae80000</link><description>Bisan Atef Owda 制作的《这是加沙的 Bisan，我还活着》获得艾美奖提名。一家亲以色列的非营利组织写了一封公开信，称 Owda 与美国指定的恐怖组织 PFLP 有“记录在案的联系”，因此不应被提名</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-group-tries-to-get-emmy-nomination-rescinded-from-palestinian-journalist/00000191-7667-dacb-afb3-ffff5ae80000</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示，拜登总统与内塔尼亚胡进行了电话交谈，副总统哈里斯也参加了通话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/president-biden-speaks-with-netanyahu-on-call-joined-by-vp-harris-white-house-says/00000191-7678-db30-a797-7e7a16c90000</link><description>拜登政府高级官员表示，布林肯本周早些时候的言论造成了一种乐观和进步的错误感觉</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:17:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/president-biden-speaks-with-netanyahu-on-call-joined-by-vp-harris-white-house-says/00000191-7678-db30-a797-7e7a16c90000</guid></item><item><title>不要评判人质家属的痛苦，或者他们表达痛苦的方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-21/ty-article/.highlight/dont-judge-the-hostage-families-pain-or-how-they-express-it/00000191-75f8-dc26-a9d7-f5f9daef0000</link><description>当人质家属希望俘虏政治敌人的孩子而不是自己的孩子时，我们应该如何应对？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-21/ty-article/.highlight/dont-judge-the-hostage-families-pain-or-how-they-express-it/00000191-75f8-dc26-a9d7-f5f9daef0000</guid></item><item><title>“政府希望以色列人过于担心自己的安全而忽视民主”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-21/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-hoping-israelis-are-too-worried-about-safety-to-think-about-democracy/00000191-6f18-d43c-af93-ff5820fc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-21/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-hoping-israelis-are-too-worried-about-safety-to-think-about-democracy/00000191-6f18-d43c-af93-ff5820fc0000</guid></item><item><title>谁是布拉德·兰德（Brad Lander），竞选纽约市长的进步犹太人和加沙停火倡导者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-progressive-jew-and-gaza-cease-fire-advocate-running-for-new-york-mayor/00000191-6a3c-deb0-ab91-ffbcd4d40000</link><description>纽约审计长布拉德·兰德 (Brad Lander) 三十年前开始了他的职业生涯，为布鲁克林受压迫的社区发声。现在，他的任务是推翻纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯(Eric Adams)，这场竞选已经受到以色列-加沙战争的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 19:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-progressive-jew-and-gaza-cease-fire-advocate-running-for-new-york-mayor/00000191-6a3c-deb0-ab91-ffbcd4d40000</guid></item><item><title>解释：费拉德尔菲和内扎里姆，这两条阻碍加沙和以色列停火的“走廊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-two-corridors-that-are-stymieing-a-gaza-israel-deal/00000191-7500-d2f3-afdf-7dd97ce70000</link><description>哈马斯长期走私武器的费城走廊沿着加沙和埃及边境延伸，而东西向的内扎里姆走廊则允许以色列军队一分为二并控制加沙地带。但哈马斯表示，如果以色列不从两国全面撤军，就不会达成人质/停火协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:55:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-two-corridors-that-are-stymieing-a-gaza-israel-deal/00000191-7500-d2f3-afdf-7dd97ce70000</guid></item><item><title>为寻求谈判突破，哈马斯向真主党施压，要求其加大对以色列的攻击力度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-deal-unlikely-hamas-looking-to-hezbollah-to-increase-pressure-on-israel/00000191-7584-d189-adbb-7d8c3cec0000</link><description>以色列、巴勒斯坦、美国和阿拉伯官员都对达成协议的可能性表示悲观，理由是内塔尼亚胡总理不断增加的要求、哈马斯不愿放弃唯一的筹码，以及叶海亚·辛瓦尔希望引发与真主党和伊朗的地区战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-deal-unlikely-hamas-looking-to-hezbollah-to-increase-pressure-on-israel/00000191-7584-d189-adbb-7d8c3cec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争第 320 天：据报道，官员称加沙停战谈判“濒临崩溃”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-320-gaza-truce-talks-on-brink-of-collapse-officials-reportedly-say/00000191-75b5-d8d0-a7bb-fdb573d00000</link><description>参与谈判的消息人士告诉国土报，内塔尼亚胡“再次破坏与哈马斯的人质释放/停火协议谈判” ■ 真主党向以色列北部发射了约 50 枚火箭，造成一名男子中度受伤 ■ 六个加沙边境社区，人质家庭论坛宣布他们将抵制政府组织的 10 月 7 日大屠杀纪念仪式 ■ 这是战争 320 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-320-gaza-truce-talks-on-brink-of-collapse-officials-reportedly-say/00000191-75b5-d8d0-a7bb-fdb573d00000</guid></item><item><title>巨型鸟类如何在空气稀薄的高空停留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/how-giant-birds-stay-aloft-at-great-heights-where-the-air-is-thin/00000191-7595-daab-a3f3-f59784c50000</link><description>在七英里高的地方，您从喷气式客机的窗户向外望去，与秃鹰四目相对。这种情况非常罕见，但确实发生了。那些秃头美女是怎么呆在上面的？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 16:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/how-giant-birds-stay-aloft-at-great-heights-where-the-air-is-thin/00000191-7595-daab-a3f3-f59784c50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列执意要拆散这些乌克兰家庭？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-is-israel-insisting-on-breaking-these-ukrainian-families-up/00000191-7401-dabe-a597-ff2bd1170000</link><description>尽管安娜在乌克兰战争中丧生的丈夫是以色列公民，但她无法在以色列获得合法地位。扎哈尔计划加入以色列国防军，像哥哥一样去加沙服役，但入籍申请未获批准</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:34:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-is-israel-insisting-on-breaking-these-ukrainian-families-up/00000191-7401-dabe-a597-ff2bd1170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前特使称联合国“没有必要，应该从地球上抹去”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-envoy-to-un-calls-it-unnecessary-and-should-be-wiped-off-the-earth/00000191-7557-dc26-a9d7-f5dfb56f0000</link><description>即将离任的以色列驻联合国大使吉拉德·埃尔丹表示，“没有哪个地方比联合国更腐败和道德扭曲了。”他在任期内习惯于发表有争议的花招和言论。他敦促各国团结起来，要求“关闭和解散”联合国</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/former-israeli-envoy-to-un-calls-it-unnecessary-and-should-be-wiped-off-the-earth/00000191-7557-dc26-a9d7-f5dfb56f0000</guid></item><item><title>因哄抬物价受到批评后，以色列航空公司将出售飞往四个目的地的固定价格机票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/following-criticism-el-al-to-sell-fixed-price-tickets-to-four-destinations/00000191-750f-daab-a3f3-f58f07f30000</link><description>该航空公司将运营飞往拉纳卡、迪拜、雅典和维也纳的固定价格航班，以色列人可以在这些地方转乘飞往其他国家的航班。该决定是在以色列航空公司首席执行官与经济部长尼尔·巴尔卡特交谈后宣布的</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 14:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/following-criticism-el-al-to-sell-fixed-price-tickets-to-four-destinations/00000191-750f-daab-a3f3-f58f07f30000</guid></item><item><title>人质母亲：哈马斯应该劫持以色列高层的儿子以换取人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/hostages-mother-hamas-should-take-sons-of-israels-top-brass-in-exchange-for-hostages/00000191-74a0-d8ab-a1f5-7efc4e2e0000</link><description>主持人为没有缩短电视直播讲话而道歉，母亲迪扎·奥尔 (Ditza Or) 在讲话中提出将她认为代表 10 月 7 日失败的人的儿子交给哈马斯</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/hostages-mother-hamas-should-take-sons-of-israels-top-brass-in-exchange-for-hostages/00000191-74a0-d8ab-a1f5-7efc4e2e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的战争目标不是人质返回。这是对加沙的占领</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-goal-is-not-the-hostages-return-its-the-occupation-of-gaza/00000191-7477-d7fc-ab93-f67774cb0000</link><description>以色列对约旦河西岸 57 年的占领告诉我们，明天不会在加沙建立任何大型犹太城市； “蠕动占领”将推动商队一个又一个商队、一个又一个前哨基地前进</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 11:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-goal-is-not-the-hostages-return-its-the-occupation-of-gaza/00000191-7477-d7fc-ab93-f67774cb0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗窃取以色列敏感数据后，以色列试图审查互联网</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</link><description>反以色列黑客窃取了大量以色列敏感数据，现在正在发布数十亿字节的秘密和机密信息。由于无法阻止黑客攻击，以色列正在发动一场徒劳的战争来阻止泄密</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-futile-war-against-massive-iranian-hack-of-secret-data/00000191-6bd7-d1ee-afb5-6bff8a510000</guid></item><item><title>来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹袭击导致以色列北部一名以色列人受伤；以色列国防军袭击真主党目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/rocket-barrage-leaves-one-wounded-in-israels-north-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000191-741c-dadb-a1f9-7cff20c70000</link><description>50 枚火箭弹猛烈攻击以色列北部，造成大面积破坏并引发火灾，导致一名男子遭受弹片和电击伤。以色列国防军发言人丹尼尔·哈加里（Daniel Hagari）表示，“真主党再次向以色列平民肆意开火”，并补充说以色列“将采取相应行动”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/.premium/rocket-barrage-leaves-one-wounded-in-israels-north-idf-strikes-hezbollah-targets/00000191-741c-dadb-a1f9-7cff20c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科学家发明了独特高效的系统来同时种植鱼类和蔬菜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/israeli-scientists-invent-revolutionary-system-to-grow-fish-and-vegetables-together/00000191-7414-dadb-a1f9-7cff28fb0000</link><description>气候变化正在给我们的食物来源带来压力。本古里安大学的科学家开发了先进的鱼菜共生系统，我们吃的蔬菜生长在我们也吃的鱼的排泄物中 - 并且它产生能量</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-21/ty-article/israeli-scientists-invent-revolutionary-system-to-grow-fish-and-vegetables-together/00000191-7414-dadb-a1f9-7cff28fb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>